"**Range:** Touch    \n"
"**Components:** V, S    \n"
"**Duration:** 8 hours \n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/spellcasting/spells/death_ward.md:17
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"You touch a creature and grant it a measure of protection from death.    \n"
"The first time the target would drop to 0 hit points as a result of taking "
"damage, the target instead drops to 1 hit point, and the spell ends.    \n"
"If the spell is still in effect when the target is subjected to an effect "
"that would kill it instantaneously without dealing damage, that effect is "
"instead negated against the target, and the spell ends. \n"
msgstr ""
